videos.description: Travis Homer breaks off a 56-yard run to the Tar Heel 4-yard line, where DeeJay Dallas finishes off the drive with a rushing TD.
videos.headline: Homer's 56-yard run sets up Miami TD

videos.description: Shaquille Quarterman causes a sack-fumble and Jonathan Garvin takes it to the house for a Miami touchdown.
videos.headline: Miami breaks out turnover chain after scoop-and-score

videos.description: Chazz Surratt fakes the handoff and dives in for a 17-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Surratt runs in for 17-yard Tar Heels' TD

videos.description: Surratt avoids a sack but throws the ball right to Joe Jackson who takes the interception 42 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Miami defense scores 2nd TD of half

videos.description: N'Kosi Perry finds Darrell Langham accross the middle for a Hurricanes' touchdown.
videos.headline: Perry connects with Langham for 5-yard TD

videos.description: N'Kosi Perry throws down the middle and is intercepted by Bryson Richardson.
videos.headline: UNC defense picks off Perry

videos.description: Chazz Surratt throws his second pick-6 of the game as Romeo Finley takes it 83 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Miami defenses scores 3rd TD of the night
